	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Karg Icebear can be found by taking the following route. Leaving Halas, turn left, follow the route towards the Permafrost. Go past where Snowflake and her gaurds are and turn right following the higher peaks on your right. Go past the right turn that takes you to the Igloos and the right after that, there is another valley where a Guard by the name of Brandl spawns and keeps watch. Here is where you can hunt as well as check for Karg. To find Karg's route, head back out away from Brandl, the way you came towards the permafrost. You go between two of three trees and then down a valley and then back up to a Plataue between two smaller peaks. These two peaks serve<BR>
as a lookout for Karg. Watch for him as his route as taken him either on the east side, west side or between these two peaks. I have managed to see and stop him twice. Both times without anything to give him or the platinum. His text does not always have the [key words] in square brackets but<BR>
I have found if you use one of the following words as the first word in your query you can get the proper reply: Who, what, where, how. and of course ending in the &quot;?&quot;. Also, if you shout the '/loc' of Karg, other will appreciate it but be warned, many will try and kill him for his own more powerful cloak and sword. So make sure you have your stuff made before giving him away. If you want or need help in the area (buffs, SoW or heals) and you see me by Brandl (where I camp to heal and meditate) give me a hail and I'll do<BR>
what I can for you. I can also show you where he's walked by me.<BR>
<BR>
Meitaintso<BR>
Shaman of the 9th season<BR>
Nameless Server<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
