			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Karg will have a misc. spawn place, but has a set path he usually follows going past Megan's tower and around the river. Bad thing is many high levels will kill him shortly after he spawns to get the prized GZ. He has about a 6-8 hour spawn rate (which sucks). I am currently trying to do a quest with him now, but haven't gotten to him while he is still alive. Also watch out for his evil twin brother Martar. Frankly I don't see why Karg has the GZ if he is necessary to complete quests especially for the newbie polarbear cloak. Well good luck.
				</font>
			</td>

