				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				UPDATE... Hehe well i tried the ole &quot;let me do quest with Karg before you kill him&quot; bit.  Luckily I found him first cuz everybody seemed to know that Karg would disappear after doing a quest with him... thus he could not be killed or fulfill others quests... just poof.  This would lead me to believe that the post above mine is yet another rumor starting &quot;i heard it from somebody... &quot; &quot;i had a friend who did it...&quot; post.  Maybe our servers are different or this was a freak occurrence, but neither is likely.  Whatever it is i'd play it safe and be the first one to him.  Yes, the werewolf in west karana spawns every night and is around the qhills zone, where EXACTLY I dont know.  Is the quest hard?  Well we're talking about a semi-rare spawn, with semi-rare loot.  Then you have to give 75pp and the werewolf claw to yet another semi-rare spawn whos killed almost the split-second he spawns.  You can do the statistics on that cuz i feel pretty damn lucky I finally got these.  Too bad Karg disappeared cuz I was gonna kill him after making me wait 4 days (about 24 hours total).  Anyway, still to this day I have only seen 4 for sale on my server, all ranging from 2.5k to 3k.  So I put mine up for 2.2k thinking i was giving a pretty good deal.  Also all my sources said get at least 2k out of them.  So after about 6 hours at bazaar over 2 days, a million tells showing interest I still had no sale.  I even had one person tell me, and i quote... &quot;those sell for about 450pp hun&quot;.  I replied &quot;for only 450 they are going in the bank&quot;.  And thats where they sit for now, and will continue to sit there as a &quot;trophy&quot; until i get my 2.2k or equivalent trade.  It took me 5 days to get these and I lucked out 3 times over.  I lucked out in getting the werewolf, its loot, and Karg.  I'm sure theres probably some lucky bastard that got these within 2 hours and others that it took 2 weeks or more.  Anyway the stats are ac4, dex+3, agi+3, weight .2, all/all.  They dont show up as anything when worn, but look really badass in your inventory slot.  I am on the Cazic Thule server if anybody is interested in them, you know the price ;).<BR>
